        django-bootstrap3
        =============================
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/dyve/django-bootstrap3.png?branch=master
            :target: https://travis-ci.org/dyve/django-bootstrap3
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-bootstrap3.png
